[[[description]]]
Checks to see if the given [zval](http://phpinternals.net/docs/zval) is a constant (see the [`IS_TYPE_CONSTANT`](http://phpinternals.net/docs/is_type_constant) type flag).

[[[additional_information]]]
This macro also has a counterpart macro, `Z_OPT_CONSTANT_P`, that accepts a pointer to a zval instead.
